      • setLogLevel

        public static void setLogLevel(String level)
                        throws IOException
        Enables logging on this level and all higher levels
        The order is, from highest to lowest:
        ERROR -> WARNING -> INFO -> DEBUG -> NONE
        Parameters:
        level - The desired log level or "None" to turn of logging
        Throws:
        IOException - Thrown if the log file could not be opened
